{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Geometry","Triangle"],"Barycentric"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Dimension","Vector","Vec3"],"Vec3"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[310,58],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Geometry/Triangle.purs","start":[310,1]},"title":"fromBarycentric"},{"children":[],"comments":"Compute barycentric coordinates of a point relative to triangle.\n\nGiven a triangle ABC and a point P, computes (u, v, w) such that:\n  P = u*A + v*B + w*C  (where u + v + w = 1)\n\nUses the standard algorithm via dot products:\n  v0 = C - A, v1 = B - A, v2 = P - A\n  d00 = v0·v0, d01 = v0·v1, d02 = v0·v2, d11 = v1·v1, d12 = v1·v2\n  denom = d00*d11 - d01*d01\n  v = (d11*d02 - d01*d12) / denom\n  w = (d00*d12 - d01*d02) / denom\n  u = 1 - v - w\n\nThree.js parity: Triangle.getBarycoord\n\nNote: For degenerate triangles (denom ≈ 0), returns centroid coordinates\nas a safe fallback rather than producing NaN/Infinity.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Geometry","Triangle"],"Triangle"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Dimension","Vector","Vec3"],"Vec3"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen",